metadata.name: Morning Glory
metadata.description:
Canon EOS 5D mkiv
Canon EF 24-105mm f/4 L IS II USM
8 seconds f/5.6, ISO 200

Image by: David Lennard

One of many sunrises I shot while staying at J Bar L Ranch in Montana's Centennial Valley. This particular morning I'd been playing around with ND filters and apertures in an effort to achieve a soft look in camera. Somehow f/5.6 worked.
